headline: WEC Energy Group (WEC): Assessing Valuation Amidst Big Investment Plans and Rising Customer Demand
summary: WEC Energy Group is drawing increased attention as demand rises across its commercial, industrial, and residential customer base. The company is preparing a massive $28 billion investment plan for the years 2025 to 2029, targeting cost-efficient solar and wind generation assets. See our latest analysis for WEC Energy Group. WEC Energy Group’s push into renewables and its 22-year streak of rising dividends have turned heads lately, especially after hitting a new 52-week high in late September...
